attributes.review: So I downloaded this a day ago and ever since then, my dog has been acting out. Throughout the day he has been sticking random decals on the walls of my house, and doing the box challenge when he thinks I’m not looking.Ofc like any functioning person, I thought nothing of it other than the dog race becoming more advanced. All up until 12:32 am last night where he came in standing like a human and told me “delete the app”. I was so confused, what app? And so I tore through my phone trying to find the app that was making both him (and possibly me) delirious. Thankfully this is the first app I deleted and everything went back the the second before I was going to download it. I got the chance to reconsider, but sadly the rewind in hours didn’t take away the mess that he made. While I’m cleaning this up I would j like to say I can’t believe the App Store would let something this unruly be easily accessible. Plz ban it, I would hate for anyone to go through what I just went through
